WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:03.280
What's our final assessment?

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:08.079
Interrogating a prisoner?

00:01:08.359 --> 00:01:09.159
An interrogation test.

00:01:10.319 --> 00:01:11.159
But don't worry.

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:12.840
The prisoner is one of our own.

00:01:16.120 --> 00:01:17.799
The files are quite thorough.

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:21.680
A Death Warrior, huh.

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:24.879
That's tough to crack.

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:26.599
Let's play it safe.

00:01:27.599 --> 00:01:28.519
Tell the prisoner,

00:01:29.239 --> 00:01:30.719
the moment Su Yang asks anything,

00:01:30.959 --> 00:01:32.120
spill everything right away.

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:33.680
Yes, I'll arrange it properly.

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:44.799
So this is a drill,

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:46.200
not the real thing, right?

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:47.200
That's right.

00:01:47.719 --> 00:01:49.640
Try asking him just one question.

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:50.640
Just one will do.

00:02:21.439 --> 00:02:23.120
Pretty convincing, indeed.

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.560
Quite realistic.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.759
Trying to fool me, huh.

00:02:59.319 --> 00:03:00.520
But his acting's pathetic.

00:03:02.439 --> 00:03:03.319
Normally,

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:05.400
I've got a few good methods

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:06.240
I could try.

00:03:07.439 --> 00:03:08.840
But they said this is a drill,

00:03:09.039 --> 00:03:10.080
no fatalities allowed.

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:11.680
So...

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.400
forget it.

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:15.479
The way I see it,

00:03:15.719 --> 00:03:16.840
Death Warriors like you

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:17.840
keep your mouths shut tight,

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.319
and you've got vicious tongues.

00:03:20.199 --> 00:03:21.240
So I won't ask you anything,

00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:22.240
and you don't need to talk.

00:03:22.599 --> 00:03:23.800
Let's just skip to the procedure.

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:25.840
I... I...

00:03:34.960 --> 00:03:35.840
Screw you!

00:03:35.879 --> 00:03:37.039
Are you out of your mind?

00:03:37.319 --> 00:03:38.520
You dare curse at me?

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:47.120
You...

00:03:47.759 --> 00:03:48.400
You...

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:50.400
You want to curse me again?

00:03:52.240 --> 00:03:53.199
Remember to see a doctor.

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:08.840
Is he here to interrogate

00:04:09.319 --> 00:04:10.719
or to silence him?

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:14.479
Did you get any results?

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.000
No.

00:04:15.319 --> 00:04:16.000
I have to admit,

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.519
he's a tough one.

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:18.519
And a great actor too.

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:20.959
He nailed the Death Warrior's defiance

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:21.879
and bitterness

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:23.639
to absolute perfection.

00:04:31.879 --> 00:04:32.839
Did you talk?

00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:34.279
I told him to screw off.

00:04:36.519 --> 00:04:37.600
Where's Su Yang?

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:39.399
The assessment's over.

00:04:39.959 --> 00:04:40.879
He went home.

00:04:42.279 --> 00:04:43.600
You know what to write, right?

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:47.839
Outwitted the prisoner,

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.560
and keenly perceived

00:04:50.439 --> 00:04:52.240
the prisoner's intent to fight back and flee.

00:04:52.639 --> 00:04:53.480
Immediately,

00:04:53.639 --> 00:04:54.639
he subdued the prisoner.

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:01.319
Get out.

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:02.920
Let me have some peace. Yes.

00:05:23.879 --> 00:05:24.759
You're upset.

00:05:26.199 --> 00:05:27.439
I was thinking,

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:29.399
in the final moments of my life,

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:31.720
I'd take good care of everyone.

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:33.519
But now,

00:05:34.319 --> 00:05:36.040
everyone's taking the risks

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.639
for my sake.

00:05:56.279 --> 00:05:57.720
I once had a younger brother.

00:06:00.199 --> 00:06:01.480
He came down with a serious illness.

00:06:02.399 --> 00:06:03.839
Roadside flyers claimed

00:06:04.639 --> 00:06:06.000
there was a miracle doctor in Shanhai City

00:06:06.600 --> 00:06:07.959
who could cure any disease.

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:09.399
So,

00:06:10.399 --> 00:06:11.639
I brought him here.

00:06:12.879 --> 00:06:14.839
Along the way, we faced wind and snow,

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:16.839
warm sunshine,

00:06:18.079 --> 00:06:18.920
seas of flowers,

00:06:20.519 --> 00:06:21.839
all filled with hope.

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:25.079
But it wasn't until we arrived in Shanhai City

00:06:26.079 --> 00:06:27.639
and met the so-called miracle doctor

00:06:29.319 --> 00:06:30.319
did I realize

00:06:31.839 --> 00:06:32.759
the wind and snow,

00:06:33.439 --> 00:06:34.240
the warm sun,

00:06:34.839 --> 00:06:35.680
the seas of flowers,

00:06:38.079 --> 00:06:39.600
none of it ever belonged to us.

00:06:41.399 --> 00:06:42.800
And your brother?

00:06:46.879 --> 00:06:47.639
Buried.

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:49.720
Sorry.

00:06:58.480 --> 00:06:59.600
I'm telling you all this

00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:01.079
just to make you understand:

00:07:01.639 --> 00:07:02.399
on Black Street,

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:04.959
everyone has something they hold onto.

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:07.319
And you

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.319
are merely the reason

00:07:09.319 --> 00:07:11.040
they stay true to themselves.

00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:14.399
From start to finish,

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:16.920
everything we've done

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:21.000
has something to do with you,

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:22.600
and yet nothing to do with you.

00:07:28.399 --> 00:07:29.040
Alright,

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:30.480
I should get going.

00:07:32.839 --> 00:07:33.759
See you in the Imperial Capital.

00:07:37.439 --> 00:07:38.720
See you in the Imperial Capital.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:56.759
I thought

00:07:56.759 --> 00:07:58.600
I'd get some juicy gossip about the cripple.

00:07:59.759 --> 00:08:01.879
Turns out it's just another dreary, miserable life story.

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:03.199
Aren't you afraid

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:05.120
the cripple will find out you eavesdropped

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:06.360
and beat you to death?

00:08:07.639 --> 00:08:08.560
Then I'll just die.

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:11.480
Is anyone on Black Street afraid of dying?

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:14.920
I am.

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:24.480
You stuffed this in my ear?

00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:26.279
Don't get mad.

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.000
Now we're even.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:37.720
So,

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:40.200
what do you plan to do next?

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:43.080
Stick to my old trade.

00:08:43.559 --> 00:08:44.519
Besides stealing,

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:46.279
I'm not good for anything.

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:49.200
I thought you'd go fight in the ring.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.240
The fighting ring?

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.159
Too crude for me.

00:09:00.039 --> 00:09:01.360
Have you been blessed?

00:09:05.519 --> 00:09:06.519
Blessed or not,

00:09:06.639 --> 00:09:08.759
what's that got to do with stealing?

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:10.759
Sit down, sit down.

00:09:11.159 --> 00:09:12.039
Don't keep standing.

00:09:13.639 --> 00:09:14.559
At the end of the day,

00:09:14.840 --> 00:09:16.399
so you haven't been blessed after all, right?

00:09:16.639 --> 00:09:17.240
What about you?

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:20.399
Are you one of the Blessed?

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:22.320
Unfortunately,

00:09:22.559 --> 00:09:23.279
I'm not either.

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:25.600
But in my view,

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.600
The Blessed

00:09:27.960 --> 00:09:29.120
aren't really all that strong.

00:09:31.679 --> 00:09:33.240
So you plan to fight in the ring?

00:09:34.919 --> 00:09:36.360
The fighting ring isn't for me.

00:09:36.799 --> 00:09:38.120
That's not my home turf.

00:09:39.440 --> 00:09:40.840
My home turf is

00:09:41.559 --> 00:09:42.919
the entire Imperial Capital.

00:09:53.919 --> 00:09:54.720
Tell me

00:09:56.639 --> 00:09:57.919
will there ever come a day

00:09:58.159 --> 00:09:59.360
when those everyday

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:02.000
robbers we look down on,

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:03.039
those petty thugs,

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.840
because of the Blessing,

00:10:04.960 --> 00:10:06.080
end up surpassing us,

00:10:07.759 --> 00:10:09.639
The things we take pride in,

00:10:10.159 --> 00:10:11.279
in their eyes,

00:10:11.799 --> 00:10:12.879
become utterly worthless?

00:10:13.759 --> 00:10:14.480
I've thought about it.

00:10:17.039 --> 00:10:18.399
Wouldn't you feel regret?

00:10:21.639 --> 00:10:22.720
That day will never come.

00:10:26.879 --> 00:10:27.559
You're right.

00:10:27.879 --> 00:10:28.559
After all, a person

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:31.159
should, at their most brilliant moment,

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:32.039
make a grand exit.

00:10:32.159 --> 00:10:33.000
That's the cool way to go.

00:10:36.559 --> 00:10:37.200
I'm off.

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:38.840
Hey, Zhou,

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:40.000
I swear I'll blow you up!

00:10:41.159 --> 00:10:42.120
See you in the Imperial Capital.

00:10:42.679 --> 00:10:43.679
If I die,

00:10:43.879 --> 00:10:44.679
my tomb

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:47.159
is in your hands.

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:55.320
Then I'll build you

00:10:55.679 --> 00:10:56.679
the grandest tomb chamber.

00:10:58.399 --> 00:10:59.080
Hold on,

00:10:59.320 --> 00:11:00.679
why are you leaving it to me?

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:09.799
Bowing out at the height of glory

00:11:10.360 --> 00:11:11.960
beats scraping by in the mud.

00:11:13.159 --> 00:11:14.240
In this life,

00:11:14.559 --> 00:11:16.360
I should stand at the top of the world.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:20.120
See you in the Imperial Capital.

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:23.039
I'm not going with you.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:28.799
You don't want to save Tongtong anymore?

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:29.679
Tongtong.

00:11:30.879 --> 00:11:31.679
Just think about it.

00:11:32.240 --> 00:11:34.679
At Tongtong's most desperate moment,

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:36.679
you descend from the sky,

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:38.919
saving Tongtong like a hero.

00:11:39.559 --> 00:11:41.039
I jump up, bam, and drop down.

00:11:41.039 --> 00:11:41.559
Right.

00:11:41.559 --> 00:11:42.960
Can I use the Overlord Fist?

00:11:42.960 --> 00:11:43.720
Sure.

00:11:43.720 --> 00:11:44.799
You can use the Overlord Fist.

00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:45.799
Let's go right now.

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:46.879
Hurry up.

00:11:47.080 --> 00:11:47.559
Okay, okay.

00:11:47.559 --> 00:11:48.240
Come on, let's go.

00:11:48.279 --> 00:11:49.039
Easy with the pulling.

00:11:49.039 --> 00:11:49.519
Hurry up.

00:11:49.519 --> 00:11:50.600
These old bones of mine...

00:11:50.600 --> 00:11:51.279
Go, go, go.

00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:09.240
After you're done watching,

00:12:09.799 --> 00:12:10.960
you really have to try

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:12.919
the oranges I bought just for you.

00:12:13.559 --> 00:12:15.200
Because not only are they fresh,

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.600
they're also incredibly...

00:12:20.960 --> 00:12:21.600
sweet.

00:12:31.799 --> 00:12:32.799
In other words,

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:35.399
I'll be taking three pawns

00:12:35.399 --> 00:12:36.320
plus one pig.

00:12:37.919 --> 00:12:40.039
As for the strength of these three pawns,

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:41.879
handling ordinary small cities

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:43.759
shouldn't be a problem.

00:12:44.279 --> 00:12:46.399
But against the other seven major cities,

00:12:46.399 --> 00:12:48.600
especially ones like the Imperial Capital,

00:12:49.039 --> 00:12:50.799
how much they can actually pull off

00:12:51.080 --> 00:12:51.960
is anyone's guess.

00:12:52.159 --> 00:12:53.279
I'm not a pig.

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:55.120
Nobody called you a pig.

00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:57.279
You're a pawn.

00:12:57.919 --> 00:12:58.600
Don't worry.

00:12:59.559 --> 00:13:00.159
Okay.

00:13:09.279 --> 00:13:10.480
These seven major cities,

00:13:10.799 --> 00:13:12.240
on the surface,

00:13:12.879 --> 00:13:13.799
seem calm and peaceful.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:15.399
But behind the scenes,

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:17.200
there's plenty of dirty business.

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:18.840
So I have reason to suspect

00:13:19.159 --> 00:13:20.240
that the real competition

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:21.799
begins the very moment

00:13:21.799 --> 00:13:22.879
we set out.

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:26.080
You're worried about ambushes on the way?

00:13:27.039 --> 00:13:27.720
Exactly.

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:30.320
Especially some ambitious smaller cities.

00:13:30.519 --> 00:13:31.679
We, the Eight Major Cities,

00:13:31.759 --> 00:13:33.480
are their biggest stumbling block.

00:13:33.799 --> 00:13:35.120
So rather than

00:13:35.320 --> 00:13:37.519
gambling on uncertainty in the fighting ring,

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:39.320
they'd rather, before the match,

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:40.240
just take us out.

00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:42.320
Most importantly,

00:13:42.840 --> 00:13:44.440
Shanhai City's army

00:13:44.519 --> 00:13:46.759
can't just leave Shanhai City's borders.

00:13:47.039 --> 00:13:48.639
Otherwise, the other cities will see it

00:13:48.639 --> 00:13:50.279
as an act of provocation.

00:13:50.720 --> 00:13:51.600
So this whole journey

00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:53.120
will be harder than you'd think.

00:13:53.919 --> 00:13:54.679
Then

00:13:56.200 --> 00:13:57.840
why don't we just take a plane?

00:13:58.159 --> 00:13:58.799
Right.

00:13:58.960 --> 00:13:59.639
Why not?

00:13:59.639 --> 00:14:00.440
Don't tell me

00:14:00.519 --> 00:14:02.399
someone can fly up to 10,000 meters

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:03.759
and blow up a plane with one punch?

00:14:11.320 --> 00:14:12.279
I'm broke.

00:14:13.679 --> 00:14:14.960
I've never flown before.

00:14:15.120 --> 00:14:17.360
So that option never crossed my mind.

00:14:20.399 --> 00:14:21.080
Question.

00:14:22.080 --> 00:14:24.519
What if someone plants a bomb on the plane?

00:14:25.399 --> 00:14:26.840
Right under his dad's nose?

00:14:26.960 --> 00:14:28.799
No one would dare pull anything in Shanhai City.

00:14:28.799 --> 00:14:29.399
Exactly.

00:14:29.399 --> 00:14:30.919
Right under my dad's nose...

00:14:31.480 --> 00:14:32.279
You know my dad?

00:14:37.200 --> 00:14:37.840
That's perfect!

00:14:38.240 --> 00:14:39.799
Then it's settled.

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:40.919
We're flying.

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:42.120
We leave in one week.

00:14:42.360 --> 00:14:44.639
This is definitely a great moneymaking opportunity.

00:14:45.240 --> 00:14:46.039
Moneymaking?

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:48.320
What moneymaking?

00:14:49.360 --> 00:14:50.240
Who said anything about money?

00:14:51.519 --> 00:14:54.879
I meant a chance to make Shanhai City famous.

00:14:55.039 --> 00:14:55.639
By the way,

00:14:57.840 --> 00:14:59.279
if during the competition

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:01.799
the Imperial Capital suddenly exploded...

00:15:05.919 --> 00:15:07.000
I just remembered,

00:15:07.320 --> 00:15:09.480
I've got some important advertisers to meet.

00:15:09.759 --> 00:15:10.559
I have to run.

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:11.399
No time to lose.

00:15:13.399 --> 00:15:14.159
Gotta go.

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:07.240
Shaping the future again, are you?

00:16:08.879 --> 00:16:09.720
But I

00:16:10.639 --> 00:16:12.360
just refuse to believe in the future.